scenarios.name: jarvis_logo
scenarios.text: The logo features a blue robot head with headphones, which is the central focus of the design. The headphones are positioned on either side of the robot's face, and they appear to be in motion or facing forward as if the robot is actively listening or engaging with something. This unique combination of elements creates an interesting visual representation that captures attention and conveys a sense of interaction between the robot and its surroundings.
